item.title: Prayer bpn12444 in Namibia
item.description: Ame, Onda pe nduka ongula ei yonena me filonghenda loYe, Kalunga kange. Ame ohai fiyepo eumbo lange nde linekela mounene woYe, ndele ohai li yandye ame mwene meameno loYe. Tuminenge, hano, onghenda yo meulu yoYe, ne nangeko noupuna ta li di kwoVe, Kwafenge opo ndi alukile vali keumbo lange me xupifo loYe. Ngashi yo kwali wa kwa fenge oku dyamo ndi li koshi yeameno loYe no madiladilo aeshe ange ota tale kwoVe.
